GCP Project Configuration
PROJECT_ID=your-gcp-project-id
REGION=asia-east2
ZONE=asia-east2-a

MTR API Configuration
MTR_API_BASE_URL=https://rt.data.gov.hk/v1/transport/mtr
MTR_API_KEY=your-api-key-here

Kafka Configuration
KAFKA_BOOTSTRAP_SERVERS=kafka:9092
KAFKA_TOPIC=mtr-arrivals
KAFKA_CONSUMER_GROUP=mtr-consumer-group

BigQuery Configuration
BIGQUERY_PROJECT=your-gcp-project-id
BIGQUERY_DATASET=mtr_analytics
BIGQUERY_TABLE=raw_arrivals

GCS Configuration
GCS_BUCKET=your-gcs-bucket-name

Spark Configuration
SPARK_MASTER=spark://spark-master:7077

Service Account (for local development)
GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=/path/to/service-account.json
